Project Title: Weather App

Description:
Developed a dynamic and responsive weather application using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The app provides real-time weather information based on user input or current location.

Key Features:

User-Friendly Interface:

Designed an intuitive and visually appealing interface for a seamless user experience.
Implemented responsive design principles to ensure compatibility across various devices.
Real-Time Weather Data:

Integrated with a weather API to fetch and display up-to-date weather information.
Supported features like temperature, humidity, wind speed, and current conditions.
Location Services:

Enabled location detection to automatically fetch weather details based on the user's current location.
Implemented a search functionality for users to manually input a location.
Forecast Display:

Provided a detailed forecast for the upcoming days, allowing users to plan ahead.
Graphical Representation:

Incorporated visual elements such as icons and charts to enhance the presentation of weather data.
Customization:

Included user preferences for metric or imperial units, catering to a global audience.
Technologies Used:

HTML for structuring the web page.
CSS for styling and layout design.
JavaScript for dynamic and interactive features.
Integration with a Weather API for real-time data.
